Agundabweni Akweyu (nke a makwaara dịka Agunda ) bụ onye amụrụ na Kenya  onye na-emepụta ihe ndekọ, onye guzobere akara ndekọ Bwenieve, onye guzobere Praise Atmosphere, onye nhazi, onye na-ede egwu, onye ọchụnta ego, onye injinia ọdịyo na di nke onye egwu ozioma Kenya bụ Evelyn Wanjiru Dabere na Nairobi Kenya, a maara ya nke ọma maka imepụta egwu maka ndị egwu guzosiri ike na ndị ka na amalite amalite
Ụdị mmepụta ya pụrụ iche ahụla mgbanwe na egwu ozioma Kenya; ọtụtụ ndị egwu na-achọ iso ya rụọ ọrụ.
